    *   Row Level Security (RLS) will be set to allow `public` read access, so the Guest (root) user can see the feed.

2.  **App Logic (`supabaseClient.tsx`)**:
    *   **Hybrid Data Source**: The client will now prefer fetching data from **Supabase** (the real DB) even for the Guest user.
    *   **Guest Mode**: The "root/root" login will remain local. It will read from the DB (to see the 5 seeded users) but its writes (likes/posts) will be simulated locally to avoid permission errors.
    *   **Fallback**: If the DB connection fails or is empty, it falls back to the internal `MOCK_` arrays.

